  "prompt": "What does it feel to see your spouse in a sex scene in a movie?",
  "response": "Seeing a spouse in a sex scene can evoke a mix of emotions\u2014excitement, pride, jealousy, and even discomfort. Some may feel proud of their partner's work and artistic expression, appreciating the opportunity for their spouse to showcase their talent. Others might feel a bit possessive or uncomfortable, as it can raise feelings of vulnerability or insecurity. Communication between partners is key in navigating these feelings, ensuring that both individuals feel respected and secure in their relationship. Ultimately, the experience can vary greatly depending on the couple's dynamics and the context of the scene.",
